::Prowl::

Prowl stands up as the CR chamber opens, walking toward Iron Raptor as she 
walks out. His eyes examine her body as she stretches, checking to make sure 
she was fully repaired. Prowl reaches Iron Raptor, his arms going around her 
waist as he leans forward to kiss her.

An excited thrill runs through him as their lips touch, Prowl's hands 
tightening around her waist.
